[2026-05-06 09:54:13 +0700] [CODEX] - **NORMAL** — full prompt with the complete `call_code_descriptions` payload (richer context, more tokens). Production default.
[2026-05-06 09:54:13 +0700] [CODEX] - **BASIC** — lean prompt variant with a reduced description set. Token-cost A/B comparator (~40% fewer tokens). Used to test whether ranking degradation under a smaller prompt is acceptable for cost savings.
