[2026-05-12 22:08:35 +0700] [CODEX] +> ### What I did
[2026-05-12 22:08:35 +0700] [CODEX] +> Through the afternoon, I rebuilt the 30-day production conversation ledger from the 9.3 GB Datadog-derived event set, carrying first and last classifier labels, tenant, YAML content hash, required rerun inputs, and local-YAML match status. I then generated the four reconciliation pivots, the source-pool ledger, the local-YAML alignment report, and the historical-YAML recovery pass instead of relying on a sampled view.
