[2026-05-12 22:08:35 +0700] [CODEX] +**Result.** The 47,153-conversation master table reconciles across code-by-company, code-by-YAML, tenant-by-YAML, and code-by-rerun-readiness pivots. The report identifies 35,319 strict rerun-ready conversations, 46,631 relaxed rerun-ready conversations, 2,166 first-vs-last classifier flips, and a 10,506-row recoverable non-current CCD cohort after historical YAML pinning.
