[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +## AGI-9466 - Pipeline Migration And Validation
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +**Why.** AGI-9466 needs repeatable generation, review, and rerun evidence for Affirm action-code acceptance criteria. The previous `vpbPostCall` layout had active code mixed with archived experiments, which made validation harder to reproduce.
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +> ### What I did
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +> That morning, I consolidated the scattered `vpbPostCall` assets into a single `vpbPostCall/` tree, promoted the active quality loop into `src/kompato/debtor/run_quality_loop_agi9466_all.py`, added the AC-DNC seed in `docs/plan/agi9466_ac_seeds.yaml`, and patched `src/kompato/debtor/agi9466_chat_arena.py` so the pipeline works with zero's older runtime. I also committed the migration locally as `9907209` and recorded the command path in `docs/AGI9466_MIGRATION_20260512.md`.
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +**Result.** Two zero-side L1 happy-path validations passed: AC-DNC reached score 5 after retry hints, and AC-001 NNP reached score 5 on the first cautious-skeptic attempt. The active loop is now the 561-line `src/kompato/debtor/run_quality_loop_agi9466_all.py`, alongside the 1,287-line chat arena implementation.
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +**Links.**
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +
