[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +- `docs/AGI9466_MIGRATION_20260512.md` - canonical path map and run command after the consolidation.
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +- `src/kompato/debtor/run_quality_loop_agi9466_all.py` - active AGI-9466 quality-loop runner.
[2026-05-12 22:08:51 +0700] [CODEX] +- `docs/plan/agi9466_ac_seeds.yaml` - acceptance-criteria seed catalog with the new AC-DNC seed.
