[2026-05-12 22:09:33 +0700] [CODEX] +
[2026-05-12 22:09:33 +0700] [CODEX] +**Why.** AGI-9466 covers Affirm disposition-code correctness. The May 12 master call-code reference removed `EPE` and `EPD`, so the local evaluation priority list and config cleanup needed a MECE check before those labels stopped being treated as active outcomes.
[2026-05-12 22:09:33 +0700] [CODEX] +
