[2026-05-12 22:09:33 +0700] [CODEX] +> That evening, I checked the May 12 master reference against the Affirm config and local priority list, wrote the EPE/EPD MECE impact note, updated `input/priority.csv`, and opened draft PR #544 from `paco-epe-epd-remove` against `dev`. The PR currently changes `scripts/en_collin_kompato_affirm/main.yaml` by 12 additions and 9 deletions at commit `0c45fb5`; its visible patch removes a stale SIF description block and hardens successful-payment postprocess handling for PAY/PIF.
