[2026-05-12 22:09:33 +0700] [CODEX] +**Result.** Draft PR #544 is open, one file changed, and CI passed. It is not merged and not yet marked review-ready because the PR body now calls out the preflight mismatch and asks reviewers to confirm whether the SIF/PIF changes should proceed or be replaced by a stricter EPE/EPD-targeted cleanup.
