[2026-05-12 22:09:34 +0700] [CODEX] +
[2026-05-12 22:09:34 +0700] [CODEX] +**Why.** DCI-333 is the all-code evaluation workstream, while DCI-334 is the broader AF postcall improvement container. Both need a reliable source pool before sampling, rerun, or Auto-QC claims can be made.
