[2026-05-12 22:10:51 +0700] [CODEX] +
[2026-05-12 22:10:51 +0700] [CODEX] +**Result.** Two zero-side L1 happy-path validations passed: AC-DNC reached score 5 after retry hints, and AC-001 NNP reached score 5 on the first cautious-skeptic attempt. The active loop is now the 561-line `src/kompato/debtor/run_quality_loop_agi9466_all.py`, alongside the 1,287-line chat arena implementation.
