[2026-05-13 22:02:19 +0700] [CODEX] 
[2026-05-13 22:02:19 +0700] [CODEX] When facts conflict, apply this precedence order:
[2026-05-13 22:02:19 +0700] [CODEX] 
[2026-05-13 22:02:19 +0700] [CODEX] 1. Latest Jira ticket status/comments/changelog for the active ticket.
