ompany hotline: 1888KOMPAT0\n    - Agent name: Chris\n\n  5. Historial Call Information:\n    ['Email sent on 03-02-2026 to email AMYGFWILLIAMS@yahoo.com with Resolve Your Account at a Reduced Balance.', 'Email sent on 03-01-2026 to email AMYGFWILLIAMS@yahoo.com with Reminder: Take Advantage of your Updated Settlement Offer for your Moneyspot USA LLC, dba Sunshine Loans Account.', \"2026-02-28 19:38:54 UTC call_id: vdJaQIbwDfN2Wx0jWUUgRw, call_code: NLM, call_status: success, summary: The call reached the customer's voicemail, and no direct contact was established. The virtual agent, Opel from Kompato AI, left a message providing a callback number and information regarding agent availability. No commitments, disputes, or payment arrangements were made during this interaction., summary_complaints: , summary_situation: , summary_verification: .\", 'SMS sent on 02-26-2026 to phone number 8476 with content: Kompato-Debt Collector: Hi we are trying to reach Amy. For more info, pls tap https://kpto.ai or call us at 18885667280. Txt STOP to opt out', \"2026-02-26 17:26:13 UTC call_id: i3YGT5IgIJxwZDb6jN9pZA, call_code: NLM, call_status: success, summary: The collector reached the consumer's voicemail, and no direct contact was established. The outgoing greeting identified the recipient as Amy and stated she would return the call at her earliest convenience. No payment commitments or disputes were discussed, and follow-up will be required., summary_complaints: , summary_situation: , summary_verification: .\", 'Email sent on 02-26-2026 to email AMYGFWILLIAMS@yahoo.com with Reduced Balance Offer Inside - A Better Way to Resolve Your Account.', 'Email sent on 02-24-2026 to email AMYGFWILLIAMS@yahoo.com with Take Advantage Of our Personalized Plan to Resolve Your Moneyspot USA LLC, dba Sunshine Loans Account.', 'Email sent on 02-22-2026 to email AMYGFWILLIAMS@yahoo.com with Amy, save $93.7 on your Moneyspot USA LLC, dba Sunshine Loans account.', 'Email sent on 02-20-2026 to ema