[2026-05-13 22:02:49 +0700] [CODEX] | `signal_level` | L1 happy path or L2 boundary/multi-signal |
[2026-05-13 22:02:49 +0700] [CODEX] | `risk_priority` | compliance, payment, transfer, admin, identity, or ops |
[2026-05-13 22:02:49 +0700] [CODEX] | `label_confidence` | Confidence band from the source ledger |
[2026-05-13 22:02:49 +0700] [CODEX] | `adjudication_source` | Deterministic prod label, major-voter queue, human, or fixture rule |
[2026-05-13 22:02:49 +0700] [CODEX] | `exclude_from_prompt_only_eval` | True for postprocess/system fixture rows |
