[2026-05-13 22:04:31 +0700] [CODEX] |---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---:|
[2026-05-13 22:04:31 +0700] [CODEX] | ALL_PAIRED | 545 | 100 | 73,919 | 7,326 | 332,931 |
[2026-05-13 22:04:31 +0700] [CODEX] | CONSISTENT | 435 | 79.82 | 143,174 | 8,667 | 332,700 |
[2026-05-13 22:04:31 +0700] [CODEX] | FLIPPED | 110 | 20.18 | 19,392 | 639 | 333,054 |
[2026-05-13 22:04:31 +0700] [CODEX] | NO_PAIR (single End event) | 756 | — | — | — | — |
