[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] ## Dimensions where fast and final differ (full reference list)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] A. **Transcript content / format** (what the classifier reads)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 1. `[stage_direction]` tags present in fast (73%), stripped in final (0%)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 2. `[company_name: Affirm]` and other `[placeholder]` tokens present in fast (63%), substituted to empty string in final — Jinja template-variable bug, not deliberate redaction
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 3. Compound `assistant:` utterances split into separate turns in final
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 4. Final transcript content extends fast for ~63% of flipped convs (AssemblyAI completes after the fast snapshot is taken)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 5. Same audio re-transcribed with different word boundaries by AssemblyAI on the second pass
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 6. `<SILENCE_5s>` count differs (more silences accumulated by final-pass time)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 7. `<ENDCALL>` marker usually in final, sometimes absent from fast
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 8. TTS phonetic leaks like `<<ə|ˈ|f|ɝ|m>>` appear in some passes only
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 9. Multilingual content (Spanish, etc.) may appear only in the final pass
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] B. **Classifier configuration** (production yaml line 5882–5888)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 10. Model: `gemini-3-flash` (yaml line 5885) — NOT gpt-4o, NOT gpt-5.5
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 11. Temperature: `0.0` (deterministic on identical input)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 12. `max_retry: 3` (retries on transient error, won't introduce variance on success)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 13. `max_tokens: 15000` (generous, not a constraint)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] C. **Surrounding prompt context**
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 14. `list_current_state` — bot state context fed to the classifier
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 15. `dict_variable` (conversation_caching) — cached insight + reflection variables
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 16. Reflection-variable values — `is_faq`, `warm_transfer`, etc.
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 17. Rule-based pre-classifier eligibility — may fire on fast snapshot, not final
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 18. YAML rendering with runtime variables (`current_time`, `user_idle_duration`)
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] D. **Pipeline-level**
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 19. YAML version drift — `ccd_hash` can change between fast and final classifier runs
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 20. Postprocess remapping — `dict_variable` signals (DTMF, payment_results, transfer_result) may not exist at fast time
[2026-05-14 22:03:18 +0700] [CODEX] 
