[2026-05-14 22:03:23 +0700] [CODEX] 
[2026-05-14 22:03:23 +0700] [CODEX] - KR1 sample-DB seed is delivered: **675 (assistant_Q, user_A) canonical exemplars across 45 codes × 3 levels × 5 each** at `output/exemplars_v2_20260514_0916/canonical_exemplars.csv`, uploaded to the team Sheet as tab `1c_intents_v2`. Cost: $1.88 total for all of today's LLM work.
[2026-05-14 22:03:23 +0700] [CODEX] - Two failed-experiment cycles preceded the win: (a) voter ensemble (yesterday) was misaligned to KR1's evidence-locator primitive, (b) Phase 1B real-conv extractor with rule-laden prompt hit only 35-50% agreement against the user's hand-graded 14-row calibration set. Both got abandoned.
