[2026-05-14 22:05:52 +0700] [CODEX] -- Canonical exemplars: delivered a review-ready seed set across the current call-code taxonomy, using authentic bot-question patterns and stronger boundary-specific prompts.
[2026-05-14 22:05:52 +0700] [CODEX] -- Fast-vs-final stability: separated instability into early rule behavior, added transcript content, version alignment, rendering sensitivity, and boundary-code overlap.
