[2026-05-14 22:05:53 +0700] [CODEX]  
[2026-05-14 22:05:53 +0700] [CODEX] -This is an acceptable compromise for KR1 because the near-term goal is balanced, reviewable coverage across the taxonomy. It is not a final truth set. The risk is that synthetic examples may be cleaner than production behavior; the control is to keep review notes, spot-check harder levels, and use real-conversation augmentation only where it adds value after the canonical seed is stable.
