[2026-05-14 22:06:29 +0700] [CODEX] -- L1 gate: require one substantive intent; rows that combine multiple code signals should be reviewed or regenerated.
[2026-05-14 22:06:29 +0700] [CODEX] -- Coverage gate: keep the seed set tied to the current call-code taxonomy and the quarter target for per-code balance.
[2026-05-14 22:06:29 +0700] [CODEX] -- Production-record gate: use final stabilized labels for reporting; keep preliminary labels as diagnostic inputs.
[2026-05-14 22:06:29 +0700] [CODEX] -- Model-alignment gate: do not publish rendering or redaction conclusions until checked against the production classifier setup.
[2026-05-14 22:06:29 +0700] [CODEX] -- Review gate: treat voter disagreement and instability as routing signals for Auto-QC, not as failures to hide.
